mayumi shintani (新谷 真弓 shintani mayumi) is a japanese voice actress and actress affiliated with nylon100. some of her major roles include tsubasa shibahime in his and her circumstances, haruko haruhara in flcl, lolo in brigadoon: marin & melan, cindy klein in earth maiden arjuna, nonon jakuzure in kill la kill and wendy in black butler: book of circus. in 2004, she portrayed scarlet claw in the live-action cutie honey film.